gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 119, Wizards 113
gameRecap.excerpt: Tyrese Maxey led the Sixers with 15 of his 28 total points in the fourth along with nine rebounds and seven assists as Buddy Hield (23 points, five rebounds, six assists) and Ricky Council IV (career-high 19 points, 10 rebounds) totaled 42 points. Tyus Jones had a season-high 25 points, nine assists, and a career-high six 3PT FG as Deni Avdija (21 points, 13 rebounds, five assists) and Kyle Kuzma (21 points, career-high four blocks) totaled 42 points. The Sixers snap a four-game skid to improve to 31-21 as the Wizards move to 9-43.
